[media]

You've heard of cowboys versus aliens - now get ready for cacti versus aliens in **Cactus Jam**! Explore a terrifying UFO to save the wild west with all your friends. Collect jam jars as you dodge, whip, and outrun alien monsters in this **fast-paced, free-to-play VR adventure.

[media]

# 🔥Why Players Can’t Get Enough: 
🎮 **A game mode for every player:** Horror, Prop Hunt, Deathmatch, Capture the Flag, and more

[media]

🌵 **Dynamic VR movement** and full-body chaos - master arm-based parkour

[media]

👽 Play as aliens, cacti, or “whatever that is” with **unlockable cosmetics**

[media]

💥 **Weekly Updates** with new content and seasonal events

[media]

👫 **Play multiplayer** with your friends in private lobbies or make new friends in public

[media]

# Keep the party going and join the jam on Discord: https://bit.ly/CactusJamDiscord
